Aim: program to convert colour image to grey and HSV


Code :

% Read the color image
colorImage = imread('beamer.jpg');

% Convert the color image to grayscale
grayImage = rgb2gray(colorImage);

% Convert the color image to HSV color space
hsvImage = rgb2hsv(colorImage);

% Display the original, grayscale, and HSV images
figure;

% Original color image
subplot(1, 3, 1);
imshow(colorImage);
title('Original Color Image');

% Grayscale image
subplot(1, 3, 2);
imshow(grayImage);
title('Grayscale Image');

% HSV color space
subplot(1, 3, 3);
imshow(hsvImage);
title('HSV Color Space');
